body:
Due to the chat restrictions, you cannot defend yourself when someone rages at you out of fear you might get restricted for defending yourself. Because of this, you just have to eat up the rage and swallow it. Gotta keep bottling it up and it&#039;s NOT healthy!!
I spent the past 5 days playing ranked, accepting the rage from my team when I was doing nothing wrong but every team needs someone to rage at and because I was the only player not talking, they chose me.

All this rage built up, and every time someone raged, I would get a massive urge to tell them where to shove it and possibly get restricted.

In the game I just played I was playing well. Always grouping when everyone else wanted too, was pretty fed too and had nice cs. Was a pretty free game until out of nowhere, my support just starts spamming chat for no reason. Raging at me for whatever reason she could think of.
I did nothing wrong all game and she just never stopped spamming caps.
&gt; &#039;&#039;ASHE!!!! WTF!!! NOOB???&#039;&#039;
&gt; &#039;&#039;ASHE!!! LEARN TO PLAY ADC NOOB!!&#039;&#039;

At one point, I stated 3 times, &#039;&#039;doing Red then getting LW then we team fight!!&#039;&#039;
I was at Red and our Aatrox was Top lane clearing a triple wave.
Leona was mid with Xerath and Rek&#039;Sai against 5 enemies. She goes in. 3v5.
They lose and die.

&gt; &#039;&#039;ASHE WTF!!! WITH TEAM F^CKING NOOB!!! WTF NOOB!!!!! REPORT THIS NOOB!!! LOOK ASHE!! LOOK AT HER!!!&#039;&#039;

Same scenario about 5 minutes later but they are bot and I am taking enemy Red to stop Graves from getting it.
She goes in 3v5 and dies, I get inhib top AND mid in exchange for their 3 deaths.

&gt; &#039;&#039;LOOK THIS F^CKING ASHE!!! DOING INHIBS WHEN WE TEAMFIGHT!!! REPORT THIS F^CKING BRONZE TROLL!!!!&#039;&#039;
&gt; &#039;&#039;F^CKING NOOB ASHE REPORT!!!&#039;&#039;

Teamfight came up, 5v5.
Aatrox, Rek&#039;Sai and Leona all go straight for their Graves (Which at this point did no damage because I crushed him bot but they focus him anyway). While doing this, their tank Amumu and tank Gragas come at us and destroy us.
I kite my way out of there, barely surviving but Xerath dies.
While focusing Graves, their midlaner killed them all. I am the only survivor with like 50HP.
&gt; &#039;&#039;THIS F^CKING ASHE AGAIN!!! ALWAYS F^CKING RUNNING!!! NEVER WITH TEAM!! NOOB NOOB NOOB NOOB!!!&#039;&#039;
&gt; &#039;&#039;I COPY ASHE!!!!!&#039;&#039;

At this point she begins to solo push top lane and does not group for the rest of game. We went top with her but she recalled and pushed bot instead. We lost 4v5.
But to the point.
After she started raging at me after that fight, I snapped. All that bottled up anger from previous games just burst out, I couldn&#039;t stop myself.
&gt; &#039;&#039;ASHE THIS! ASHE THAT!!!! ASHE F^CKING THIS!! ASHE F^CKING THAT!!!!&#039;&#039;
&gt; &#039;&#039;TRY FOCUSING ON YOUR OWN SH^TTY F^CKING GAMEPLAY BEFORE CRYING ABOUT ME!!!&#039;&#039;
&gt; &#039;&#039;NOT ONCE HAVE YOU PROTECTED ME OR XERATH ALL GAME!! ALWAYS F^CKING OPEN KAT!!!!&#039;&#039;
&gt; &#039;&#039;KAT WALKS UP TO US AND JUST INSTAKILLS US BECAUSE YOU ARE NOT DOING YOUR F^CKING JOB!!!&#039;&#039;
&gt; &#039;&#039;DO YOUR F^CKING JOB BEFORE COMMENTING ON MINE!!!&#039;&#039;
&gt; &#039;&#039;F^CKING TOXIC D^CK!!!&#039;&#039;
&gt; &#039;&#039;SHUT!!&#039;&#039;
&gt; &#039;&#039;THE!!!&#039;&#039;
&gt; &#039;&#039;F^CK!!!&#039;&#039;
&gt; &#039;&#039;UP!!!!!&#039;&#039;


Yup.
I snapped.
That is about 5 days of built of rage gathered in solo queue. If in previous games I could have said 
&gt; &#039;&#039;Dude, stop crying about me. You pushed with no wards and got punished for it. It&#039;s not my fault&#039;&#039;
Then I would not have snapped. But the above sentence is enough to warrant a report in solo queue because everyone is so super sensitive and I don&#039;t want a restriction on my account. Due to that, I had to bottle up all the hate and it eventually overwhelmed me.
The Chat Restriction System is unhealthy and broken.
I genuinely fear, that I log in tomorrow with a nice chat restriction message.

Apologies for the wall of text.
If you didn&#039;t read, fair enough.
Just wanted to vent somewhere about my hatred for this broken report system.

Riot, do something about this please.
I get raged at for 5 days and I say nothing. I rage in 1 game against a super toxic kid and I&#039;m probably getting restricted because of it.
This system makes no sense :/
